*PPD-Adobe: "4.3"
*FormatVersion: "4.3"
*FileVersion: "1.0"
*LanguageVersion: English
*LanguageEncoding: ISOLatin1
*ModelName: "LJ MFP 001"
*ShortNickName: "LJ MFP 001"
*NickName: "LJ MFP 001 Localization Sample"
*Manufacturer: "ACME"
*cupsLanguages: "en zh_CN"

*OpenUI *PageSize/Media Size: PickOne
*DefaultPageSize: A4
*PageSize A4/A4: "<</PageSize[595 842]>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize Letter/US Letter: "<</PageSize[612 792]>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *PageSize

*OpenUI *Duplex/Two-Sided Printing: PickOne
*DefaultDuplex: None
*Duplex None/Off: "<</Duplex false>>setpagedevice"
*Duplex DuplexNoTumble/Long-Edge Binding: "<</Duplex true/Tumble false>>setpagedevice"
*Duplex DuplexTumble/Short-Edge Binding: "<</Duplex true/Tumble true>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *Duplex

*OpenUI *ColorModel/Color Mode: PickOne
*DefaultColorModel: Gray
*ColorModel Gray/Grayscale: "<</cupsColorSpace 0>>setpagedevice"
*ColorModel RGB/Color: "<</cupsColorSpace 1>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *ColorModel

*OpenUI *Resolution/Resolution: PickOne
*DefaultResolution: 600dpi
*Resolution 600dpi/600 dpi: "<</HWResolution[600 600]>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *Resolution

*OpenUI *Collate/Collate: PickOne
*DefaultCollate: True
*Collate True/On: ""
*CloseUI: *Collate

*OpenUI *MediaType/Media Type: PickOne
*DefaultMediaType: Plain
*MediaType Plain/Plain Paper: ""
*CloseUI: *MediaType

*% ---------------- zh_CN 本地化 ----------------
*zh_CN.Translation PageSize/纸张尺寸: ""
*zh_CN.PageSize A4/A4: ""
*zh_CN.PageSize Letter/信纸: ""

*zh_CN.Translation Duplex/双面打印: ""
*zh_CN.Duplex None/关闭: ""
*zh_CN.Duplex DuplexNoTumble/长边装订: ""
*zh_CN.Duplex DuplexTumble/短边装…: ""

*zh_CN.Translation ColorModel/颜色模式: ""
*zh_CN.ColorModel Gray/灰阶: ""
*% 注意: ColorModel RGB 的 zh_CN 本地化故意缺失

*zh_CN.Translation Resolution/分辨率: ""
*zh_CN.Resolution 600dpi/600 dpi�: ""

*zh_CN.Translation Collate/逐份打印: ""
*zh_CN.Collate True/逐份: ""

*zh_CN.Translation MediaType/介质类型: ""
*zh_CN.MediaType Plain/普通纸: ""

*% End of PPD
